# Implementation Plan - Refactor execution of Main.go

Refactor [cmd/server/main.go](file:///c:/coding/futuresign/futuresign_monorepo/backend-go/cmd/server/main.go) to improve maintainability by moving route configuration into a dedicated `internal/router` package.

## Proposed Changes

### [NEW] `internal/router/`
Create a new package to handle all routing logic.

#### [NEW] `internal/router/router.go`
- Define a `Router` struct or function that accepts the Gin engine and necessary dependencies (mostly Handlers).
- This file will act as the entry point for all route registrations.

#### [NEW] `internal/router/user_routes.go`
- Move [setupUserRoutes](file:///c:/coding/futuresign/futuresign_monorepo/backend-go/cmd/server/main.go#736-769) from [main.go](file:///c:/coding/futuresign/futuresign_monorepo/backend-go/cmd/server/main.go) to here.
- Function signature: `func (r *Router) RegisterUserRoutes(v1 *gin.RouterGroup, userHandler *handler.UserHandler)` or similar.

#### [NEW] `internal/router/member_routes.go`
- Move [setupMemberRoutes](file:///c:/coding/futuresign/futuresign_monorepo/backend-go/cmd/server/main.go#770-807) to here.

### [MODIFY] [cmd/server/main.go](file:///c:/coding/futuresign/futuresign_monorepo/backend-go/cmd/server/main.go)
- Remove [setupUserRoutes](file:///c:/coding/futuresign/futuresign_monorepo/backend-go/cmd/server/main.go#736-769), [setupMemberRoutes](file:///c:/coding/futuresign/futuresign_monorepo/backend-go/cmd/server/main.go#770-807), etc.
- Remove [setupRoutes](file:///c:/coding/futuresign/futuresign_monorepo/backend-go/cmd/server/main.go#211-294) function body (replace with calls to `internal/router`).
- Initialize the `router` package and call its setup methods.

